OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and warm day with hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine throughout. The wind will
OL,7,Fstart off light but will pick-up
OL,8,Fslightly from late morning before
OL,9,Feasing once more by the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mild night with cloud
OL,12,Fthickening and outbreaks of patchy
OL,13,Frain for some with a light breeze. The
OL,14,Frain clearing to give clear spells by
OL,15,Fdawn.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FPatchy cloud to start will
OL,18,Fgive way to some sunny spells and
OL,19,Flight winds. Warm for most places, a
OL,20,Flittle cooler along coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
