OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FLargely
OL,6,Fbright and sunny throughout and
OL,7,Ffeeling very warm or hot for most, a
OL,8,Flittle cooler near coasts with an
OL,9,Fonshore flow.
